Simple to set up and easy to use with material-thickness stops for common DIY materials: 1/2\", 3/4\", 1 1/2\"</li>\r\n<li>Durable construction to last for years, with lifetime drill-guide warranty</li>\r\n<li>Included Drill Guide Spacer works with Pocket-Hole Jig 310 and 320</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>',NULL,'<h2 id=\"anchor-specchart\" class=\"title d-none d-sm-block\">Specifications</h2><div id=\"collapsible-specs-1\" class=\"value content\"><div class=\"specifications-section specifications-tables\"><div class=\"table-container single-table\"><h5>Technical Specifications</h5><table><tbody><tr><th>Features</th><td><ul><li>Creates additional hole-drilling and spacing options for Kreg Jig 310 and 320</li><li>Adds another pocket-hole drill guide</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th>Construction</th><td>Durable plastic polymer, hardened steel</td></tr><tr><th>Adjustability</th><td>Adjustable material-thickness stops at 1/2\", 3/4\", 1 1/2\"</td></tr><tr><th>Capacity</th><td>Materials from 1/2\"- to 1 1/2\"-thick</td></tr><tr><th>Compatibility</th><td><ul><li>Pocket-Hole Jig 320</li><li>Pocket-Hole Jig 310</li><li>Kreg Pocket-Hole Screws</li><li>Kreg Pocket-Hole Plugs</li><li>Easy-Set Drill Bit, Stop Collar, Wrench</li><li>Pocket-Hole Jig Universal Clamp Adapter</li><li>Pocket-Hole Jig Spacers</li><li>Easy-Set Material-Thickness Gauge/Wrench</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th>Includes</th><td><ul><li>(1) Drill Guide with Material Thickness Stop</li><li>(1) Drill Guide Spacer</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th>Warranty</th><td>Lifetime drill-guide warranty</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div>','','Expand the capability of your Kreg&reg; Pocket-Hole Jig 310 or 320. The Pocket-Hole Jig Expansion Pack includes one hardened-steel drill guide&mdash;with thickness stops for 1/2\", 3/4\", 1 1/2\" material&mdash;for increased pocket-hole capacity, plus a Pocket-Hole Jig Spacer that provides more pocket-hole spacing options.',NULL,'KPHA110','Kreg® Pocket-Hole Jig Expansion Pack',NULL,350,'In Stock',9,0,NULL,0,67,'kpha110',1,'1606829941.jpg',NULL,NULL,100,NULL,'2020-12-01 12:39:01','2023-01-24 22:38:14'),(36,NULL,'<h2 id=\"anchor-product-details\" class=\"title d-none d-sm-block\">Product Details</h2>\r\n<div id=\"collapsible-details-1\" class=\"value content\">\r\n<p><strong>Create hole-spacing options for Kreg&reg; Pocket-Hole Jig 310 and 320</strong><br />Expand the capability of your Kreg&reg; Pocket-Hole Jig 320 by adding more hole-spacing options. This kit includes two Pocket-Hole Jig Spacers that fit between the drill guides, so you can easily increase the spacing between holes by 3/4\" increments to match your project needs. The spacers fit in place beside the drill guides, or beside another spacer, and lock into place with a simple twist.</p>\r\n</div>',NULL,'<h2 id=\"anchor-specchart\" class=\"title d-none d-sm-block\">Specifications</h2><div id=\"collapsible-specs-1\" class=\"value content\"><div class=\"specifications-section specifications-tables\"><div class=\"table-container single-table\"><h5>Technical Specifications</h5><table><tbody><tr><th>Features</th><td>Creates additional hole-drilling and spacing options for Kreg Jig 310 and 320</td></tr><tr><th>Construction</th><td>Durable plastic polymer</td></tr><tr><th>Compatibility</th><td><ul><li>Pocket-Hole Jig 320</li><li>Pocket-Hole Jig 310</li><li>Pocket-Hole Jig Universal Clamp Adapter</li><li>Pocket-Hole Jig Expansion Pack</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th>Includes</th><td>(2) Drill Guide Spacers</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div>','','Expand the capability of your Kreg&reg; Pocket-Hole Jig 320 by adding more hole-spacing options. This kit includes two Pocket-Hole Jig Spacers that fit between the drill guides, so you can easily increase the spacing between holes to match your project needs.',NULL,'KPHA120','Kreg® Pocket-Hole Jig Spacers',NULL,174,'In Stock',9,0,NULL,0,67,'kpha120',1,'1606831079.jpg',NULL,NULL,100,NULL,'2020-12-01 12:57:59','2023-01-24 22:38:14'),(37,NULL,'<h2 id=\"anchor-product-details\" class=\"title d-none d-sm-block\">Product Details</h2>\r\n<div id=\"collapsible-details-1\" class=\"value content\">\r\n<p><strong>Clamp Adapter for Kreg&reg; Pocket-Hole Jig 320, 310</strong><br />Make it even easier to hold your Kreg&reg; 300-Series Pocket-Hole Jig in position as you work using the Universal Clamp Adapter. The Universal Clamp Adapter fits into the drill guide and accepts any Kreg Clamp, as well as most trigger-action clamps. The adapter locks onto the clamp and, so the jig is held securely, and you can move and position the jig using just one hand.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Attaches easily to Drill Guide or Drill Guide Spacer</li>\r\n<li>Works with Kreg&reg; clamps, as well as trigger-action clamps and others</li>\r\n<li>Holds clamp in place on jig to allow one-handed jig placement on workpiece</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>',NULL,'<h2 id=\"anchor-specchart\" class=\"title d-none d-sm-block\">Specifications</h2><div id=\"collapsible-specs-1\" class=\"value content\"><div class=\"specifications-section specifications-tables\"><div class=\"table-container single-table\"><h5>Technical Specifications</h5><table><tbody><tr><th>Features</th><td><ul><li>Attaches easily to Drill Guide or Drill Guide Spacer</li><li>Holds clamp in place on jig</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th>Construction</th><td>Durable plastic polymer</td></tr><tr><th>Adjustability</th><td>Jaws slide and lock in place to fit different clamps.</td></tr><tr><th>Compatibility</th><td><ul><li>Pocket-Hole Jig 320</li><li>Pocket-Hole Jig 310</li><li>Works with Kreg clamps and others</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th>Includes</th><td>(1) Universal Clamp Adapter</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div>','','Make it even easier to hold your Kreg&reg; 300 Series Pocket-Hole Jig in position as you work using the Universal Clamp Adapter. It accepts any Kreg Clamp, as well as most trigger-action clamps, and grips the clamp for easy one-handed jig positioning.',NULL,'KPHA150','Kreg® Pocket-Hole Jig Universal Clamp Adapter',NULL,80,'In Stock',9,0,NULL,0,67,'kpha150',1,'1607105106.jpg',NULL,NULL,100,NULL,'2020-12-04 17:01:20','2023-01-24 22:38:14'),(38,NULL,'<h2 id=\"anchor-product-details\" class=\"title d-none d-sm-block\">Product Details</h2>\r\n<div id=\"collapsible-details-1\" class=\"value content\">\r\n<p>This kit includes the same Easy-Set Stop Collar and Material Thickness Gauge/Hex Wrench that come with Kreg&reg; 300-Series Pocket-Hole Jigs. The collar features a window that aligns with the engraved markings on the Kreg Easy-Set Pocket-Hole Drill Bit to make setting the bit at the correct depth easy for 1/2\", 3/4\", and 1 1/2\" materials. The Material Thickness Gauge allows you to easily determine material thickness (1/2\", 3/4\", 1 1/2\"), and has a built-in hex wrench for tightening the stop collar. Collar also fits all other standard (3/8\"-diameter) Kreg pocket-hole drill bits.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Stop collar and Material-Thickness Gauge/Hex wrench for Kreg&reg; Pocket-Hole Jigs</li>\r\n<li>Stop collar window aligns with etched markings on drill bit for easy setup</li>\r\n<li>Thickness Gauge easily measures material thickness (1/2\", 3/4\", 1 1/2\"), and has built-in hex wrench</li>\r\n<li>Direct replacement for items included with Kreg&reg; Pocket-Hole Jig 320, 310</li>\r\n<li>Also works with K5, K4, K3, R3, Mini, and Foreman (DB210)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>',NULL,'<h2 id=\"anchor-specchart\" class=\"title d-none d-sm-block\">Specifications</h2><div id=\"collapsible-specs-1\" class=\"value content\"><div class=\"specifications-section specifications-tables\"><div class=\"table-container single-table\"><h5>Technical Specifications</h5><table><tbody><tr><th>Features</th><td>Direct replacement for stop collar and thickness gauge/wrench included with Kreg&reg; Pocket-Hole Jig 320, 310</td></tr><tr><th>Construction</th><td>Steel, plastic polymer</td></tr><tr><th>Capacity</th><td>Thickness Gauge measures 1/2\"-1 1/2\" thicknesses</td></tr><tr><th>Compatibility</th><td><ul><li>Easy-Set Pcoket Hole Drill Bit</li><li>Pocket-Hole Jig 320, 310</li><li>Works with all Kreg Pocket-Hole Jigs and drill bits</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th>Includes</th><td><ul><li>(1) Easy-Set Stop Collar</li><li>(1) Material Thickness Gauge/Hex Wrench</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div>','','This kit includes the same Easy-Set Stop Collar and Material Thickness Gauge/Hex Wrench that come with Kreg&reg; 300-Series Pocket-Hole Jigs. The collar features a window that aligns with the engraved markings on the Kreg Easy-Set Pocket-Hole Drill Bit. The Material Thickness Gauge allows you to easily determine material thickness (1/2\", 3/4\", 1 1/2\"), and has a built-in hex wrench for tightening the stop collar',NULL,'KPHA330','Kreg® Easy-Set Stop Collar & Material Thickness Gauge/Hex Wrench Kit',NULL,90,'In Stock',9,0,NULL,0,67,'kpha330',1,'1607105441.jpg',NULL,NULL,100,NULL,'2020-12-04 17:10:41','2023-01-24 22:38:14'),(39,NULL,'<h2 id=\"anchor-product-details\" class=\"title d-none d-sm-block\">Product Details</h2>\r\n<div id=\"collapsible-details-1\" class=\"value content\">\r\n<p><strong>Take your Kreg Joinery projects to the next level by creating custom plugs from any wood species</strong><br />With the Custom Pocket-Hole Plug Cutter, you can use pocket-hole joinery virtually anywhere &mdash; even in places that show prominently on your project &mdash; by hiding the pocket holes with perfectly matched plugs that you create from any wood you desire. Plus, the Custom Pocket-Hole Plug Cutter allows you to create face grain plugs that that blend in amazingly well, whether the plugs are in line with the grain, or they run across the grain. These face grain plugs are easier to hide than conventional plugs that have visible end-grain.</p>\r\n<p>In addition, the Custom Pocket-Hole Plug Cutter also accepts accessory bits (sold separately) that can cut plugs that fit Kreg Micro-Pocket&trade; pocket holes, as well as plugs to work with the Kreg Jig&reg; HD &mdash; a plug size that&rsquo;s only possible using the Custom Pocket-Hole Plug Cutter. The Plug Cutter simply slips into a Kreg Pocket-Hole Jig in place of the normal drill guide block, and works with a Pocket-Hole Jig K5, K4, or K3 model. That allows you to clamp your plug material in place and drill in the same way that is used for creating pocket holes. To create the plugs, just chuck the plug cutting bit into any drill.</p>\r\n<p>This high-performance bit features a specially designed cutting tip that shears cleanly for a smooth, consistent plug. Fluting reduces heat and friction for better plugs and longer bit life, while a positive stop collar ensures perfect depth every time to produce accurately sized plugs. Once the plugs are drilled, they can easily be cut free using a band saw or hand saw.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Fits into Pocket-Hole Jigs K3, K4, or K5</li>\r\n<li>Hardened-steel drill guides provide reliable drilling and feature a lifetime warranty</li>\r\n<li>Works with standard Plug Cutting Bit (included)</li>\r\n<li>Works with HD and Micro Bits (sold separately)</li>\r\n<li>Bit tip shears wood fibers cleanly to create a smooth, consistent plug</li>\r\n<li>Special fluting reduces heat and friction for better plugs and longer bit life</li>\r\n<li>Open design ensures easy plug release</li>\r\n<li><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/xn4ZnA5ERBk\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>',NULL,'<h2 id=\"anchor-specchart\" class=\"title d-none d-sm-block\">Specifications</h2><div id=\"collapsible-specs-1\" class=\"value content\"><div class=\"specifications-section specifications-manuals\"><h5>Manuals</h5><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.kregtool.com/on/demandware.static/-/Library-Sites-RefArchSharedLibrary/default/dw6920b6a3/manuals/KPCS_NA.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">&nbsp;North American Manual</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"specifications-section specifications-tables\"><div class=\"table-container single-table\"><h5>Technical Specifications</h5><table><tbody><tr><th>Features</th><td>Creates custom pocket-hole plugs in three sizes</td></tr><tr><th>Construction</th><td>Glass-reinforced nylon, hardened steel</td></tr><tr><th>Compatibility</th><td><ul><li>Pocket-Hole Jig K5, K4, K3</li><li>Custom Plug Cutting Bit</li><li>Custom Plug Cutting Bit - Micro</li><li>Custom Plug Cutting Bit - HD</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th>Includes</th><td><ul><li>(1) Custom Pocket-Hole Plug Cutter</li><li>(1) Custom Plug Cutting Bit (for standard-size pocket holes)</li><li>(1) Stop collar with hex wrench</li><li>Owner\'s Manual</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th>Warranty</th><td>Lifetime drill-guide warranty</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div>','','<ul>\r\n<li>Fits into Pocket-Hole Jigs K3, K4, or K5</li>\r\n<li>Hardened-steel drill guides provide reliable drilling and feature a lifetime warranty</li>\r\n<li>Works with standard Plug Cutting Bit (included)</li>\r\n<li>Works with HD and Micro Bits (sold separately)</li>\r\n<li>Bit tip shears wood fibers cleanly to create a smooth, consistent plug</li>\r\n<li>Special fluting reduces heat and friction for better plugs and longer bit life</li>\r\n<li>Open design ensures easy plug release</li>\r\n</ul>',NULL,'KPCS','Custom Pocket-Hole Plug Cutter',NULL,1499,'In Stock',9,0,39,0,67,'kpcs',1,'1607105969.jpg',NULL,NULL,100,NULL,'2020-12-04 17:19:29','2023-01-24 22:38:14'),(40,NULL,'<h2 id=\"anchor-product-details\" class=\"title d-none d-sm-block\">Product Details</h2>\r\n<div id=\"collapsible-details-1\" class=\"value content\">\r\n<p><strong>Create More Compact Pocket Holes in the Same Kreg Joinery Applications</strong><br />With a 25% smaller hole diameter, the Micro-Pocket&trade; Drill Guide lets you create compact, low-profile pocket holes in the same Kreg Joinery applications where you\'d use standard Kreg pocket holes, and in a variety of other applications, too. You also have the ability to tackle smaller projects, thinner stock, and tighter repairs where standard pocket holes simply can&rsquo;t go.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Choose Your Jig</strong><br />Compatible with the Kreg Pocket-Hole Jig K3, K4, K4MS, K5 and K5MS. Features black color to differentiate from the standard Kreg Drill Guide.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Endless Applications</strong><br />A 25% smaller pocket hole works great in virtually every application where you&rsquo;d use standard Kreg pocket holes. And because it removes less material, drill strokes are faster and easier.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Perfect for 1/2\" Stock</strong><br />Screw heads seat well below material surface in thin stock, making the Micro-Pocket&trade; Drill Guide perfect for creating fully-pluggable pocket holes in 1/2\" (12mm) thick material like drawer boxes.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Perfect for Narrow Stock</strong><br />Reduced width lets you drill two holes in extremely narrow stock, down to 1\" wide, creating a much stronger joint in narrow pieces.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>25% smaller pocket-hole diameter</li>\r\n<li>Great for smaller projects, thinner stock, and repair applications</li>\r\n<li>Compatible with the Kreg Pocket-Hole Jig K3, K4, K4MS, K5 and K5MS</li>\r\n<li>Features black color to differentiate from standard Kreg Drill Guide</li>\r\n<li>Works with 1/2\" (12mm) stock and narrow stock, down to 1\" (25mm) wide</li>\r\n<li>Works with Kreg Pan-Head Pocket-Hole Screws (SPS)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>',NULL,'','','<ul>\r\n<li>25% smaller pocket-hole diameter</li>\r\n<li>Great for smaller projects, thinner stock, and repair applications</li>\r\n<li>Compatible with the Kreg Pocket-Hole Jig K3, K4, K4MS, K5 and K5MS</li>\r\n<li>Features black color to differentiate from standard Kreg Drill Guide</li>\r\n<li>Works with 1/2\" (12mm) stock and narrow stock, down to 1\" (25mm) wide</li>\r\n<li>Works with Kreg Pan-Head Pocket-Hole Screws (SPS)</li>\r\n</ul>',NULL,'KJMICRODGB','Micro-Pocket™ Drill Guide',NULL,974,'In Stock',9,0,NULL,0,67,'kjmicrodgb',1,'1607