d>SML-C125-250</td><td>Indoor</td><td>Zinc with Coarse Thread and Maxi-Loc Head</td><td>1 1/4\"</td></tr></tbody></table><br /><table><tbody><tr><td><ul><li>Kreg&reg; Pocket-Hole Jigs</li><li>Pocket-hole Machines</li><li>Kreg&reg; Square-Drive Bits</li></ul></td><td>(250) Zinc Pocket-Hole Screws</td></tr></tbody></table>','<table><tbody><tr><td>SML-C125-250</td><td>Indoor</td><td>Zinc with Coarse Thread and Maxi-Loc Head</td><td>1 1/4\"</td></tr></tbody></table><br /><table><tbody><tr><td><ul><li>Kreg&reg; Pocket-Hole Jigs</li><li>Pocket-hole Machines</li><li>Kreg&reg; Square-Drive Bits</li></ul></td><td>(250) Zinc Pocket-Hole Screws</td></tr></tbody></table>','KREG&reg; Zinc Pocket-Hole Screws - 32mm/1.25\", #8 Coarse-Thread, Maxi-Loc&trade;, 250-count',NULL,'SML-C125-250-INT','Zinc Pocket-Hole Screws',NULL,174,'In Stock',9,0,NULL,0,71,'sml-c125-250-int',1,'1607372262.jpg',NULL,NULL,100,NULL,'2020-12-07 19:17:42','2023-01-24 22:38:14'),(51,NULL,'<h2 id=\"anchor-product-details\" class=\"title d-none d-sm-block\">Product Details</h2>\r\n<div id=\"collapsible-details-1\" class=\"value content\">\r\n<p>The Right Angle Clamp makes projects with 90&deg; joints faster and easier than ever by giving you the helping hand you need to hold the parts in position as you drive in the screws. Just slip the pin on the Right Angle Clamp into a pocket hole, close the clamp, and it draws the mating pieces tightly together. The swiveling clamp pad opposite the pin grabs the mating piece securely. Thanks to Automaxx&reg; auto-adjust technology, the Right Angle Clamp adjusts to match the material automatically with a simple squeeze of the handles. This handy clamp works with all kinds of materials, from thin 1/2\" plywood to thick 2x4 boards.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Clamp Using the Pocket Hole</strong><br />The steel pin on this clamp is shaped to fit snugly into a pocket hole, securely anchoring one workpiece against the other for easy assembly. Just drive a screw into an adjacent pocket hole while the Right Angle Clamp holds the piece steady for you.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Swivel Pad for Solid Clamping</strong><br />The arm opposite the pin features a pad that swivels to fit tight against your material, so you can count on solid clamping without a chance of the joint shifting.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Ultra-Wide Reach</strong><br />Whether you&rsquo;re joining two thin drawer sides for a cabinet, or thicker materials to frame an outdoor project, the Right Angle Clamp opens wide to get the job done.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Use One Clamp, or Use Two</strong><br />Many woodworkers find it handy to use two Right Angle Clamps when assembling large workpieces. Place a clamp on each end to hold the wood while you drive screws in the remaining pocket holes.</p>\r\n</div>',NULL,'<h2 id=\"anchor-specchart\" class=\"title d-none d-sm-block\">Specifications</h2><div id=\"collapsible-specs-1\" class=\"value content\"><div class=\"specifications-section specifications-tables\"><div class=\"table-container single-table\"><h5>Technical Specifications</h5><table><tbody><tr><th>Features</th><td>Automaxx&reg; auto-adjust technology</td></tr><tr><th>Construction</th><td>Steel with padded grips</td></tr><tr><th>Adjustability</th><td>Adjustable clamping pressure</td></tr><tr><th>Capacity</th><td><ul><li>Clamping capacity up to 3 1/8\" (79 mm)</li><li>5\" (127 mm) reach</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div>','','<ul>\r\n<li>Holds pocket-hole joints at 90&deg; during project assembly</li>\r\n<li>Automaxx&reg; technology adjusts automatically to material thickness</li>\r\n<li>Contoured grips for added comfort</li>\r\n<li>Pin fits securely into pocket hole</li>\r\n<li>Swivel pad holds mating piece</li>\r\n<li>5\" (127mm) reach</li>\r\n</ul>',NULL,'KHCRA','Right Angle Clamp',NULL,700,'In Stock',9,0,NULL,0,33,'khcra',1,'1607373152.jpg',NULL,NULL,100,NULL,'2020-12-07 19:32:32','2023-01-24 22:38:14'),(52,NULL,'<h2 id=\"anchor-product-details\" class=\"title d-none d-sm-block\">Product Details</h2>\r\n<div id=\"collapsible-details-1\" class=\"value content\">\r\n<p>The Kreg&reg; 90&deg; Corner Clamp gives you the helping hand you need to hold 90&deg; corners and \"T\" joints together securely when you&rsquo;re assembling boxes, drawers, cabinets and cases. Plus, the 90&deg; Corner Clamp leaves both of your hands free to add your fasteners. The 90&deg; Corner Clamp is the fastest, easiest-to-use corner clamp you can buy thanks to Kreg Automaxx&reg; auto-adjusting technology.</p>\r\n<p>The 90&deg; Corner Clamp helps hold assemblies like boxes, cabinets, drawers, and cases together to ensure that you get strong, tight-fitting assemblies &mdash; whether you&rsquo;re using Kreg pocket-hole joinery, or another method. The clamp&rsquo;s V-wedge jaws grip the mating pieces securely, ensuring that the pieces sit at precise 90&deg; angles while you drive in Kreg Screws, or even another type of fastener, such as a nail or wood screw.</p>\r\n<p>The 90&deg; Corner Clamp features all-metal construction, including cast-aluminum pads &mdash; an outer \"V\" and inner wedge &mdash; that press against the inside and outside faces of the two pieces being joined in order to hold those pieces at a 90&deg; angle to one another. Edge stops also help align the edges of the pieces to ensure accurate assembly of structures like boxes, cabinets, drawers, and cases.</p>\r\n<p>Thanks to Automaxx&reg; auto-adjust technology, all you have to do is squeeze the clamp handles. The clamp will automatically close with the amount of pressure you have set, regardless of the material, whether you&rsquo;re using thin plywood for drawers, or materials up to 1\" thick.<br /><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/ouoyk5zjuBc\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n</div>',NULL,'<h2 id=\"anchor-specchart\" class=\"title d-none d-sm-block\">Specifications</h2><div id=\"collapsible-specs-1\" class=\"value content\"><div class=\"s